	" Desync information
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"The emulator used was 
	[a class=intlink href=/Http://Files.filefront.com/Vbav17zip/;9295075;/Fileinfo 
		"VBA 1.7.2 v17
	]a
	". 
	[b 
		"The movie will not work in any later version (v18+).
	]b
	" The movie may work in earlier versions.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"To make sure the movie does not desync, follow these steps:
	$LF
]p
[ol 
	[li 
		" Make sure VBA is closed, and delete the .sav file.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Set the system clock to May 19 (doesn't seem to matter which year). Some other dates work.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Open VBA and play the movie.
		$LF
	]li
]ol
[p 
	"If for some reason that still doesn't work, use one of the savestates. The first one is 
	[tt 
		"beginning.sgm
	]tt
